    25	      satisfied_by_current_adapter: partial
    26	      evidence_ref: "STATE.md:884 — earlier flow-field PNG showed Baughn Re=23750 regime but case was at Re=10000; geometry/regime mismatch history. Recent phase-7 regeneration pass likely corrected this, but it's a pattern to check."
    27	  contract_status: "INCOMPATIBLE_WITH_LITERATURE_DISGUISED_AS_COMPATIBLE — two independent physics hazards compound: (1) adapter produces a 2D planar slice, not an axisymmetric wedge; (2) the buoyantFoam solver-config under-converges (A4 p_rgh iteration-cap is the observable symptom; root cause queued for Phase 9 solver-config audit — under-relaxation, p-v coupling, thermal BC consistency, axis treatment all in scope). Prior fixture reported ref_value=0.0042 which is dimensionally Cf, not Nusselt — pure value-leakage into the wrong observable. A PASS on this case today is vacuous."
